      "content": "it's not just about the dishes or being tired. it's like the purpose is just gone. i spent years taking care of him, and now that he's gone, i'm just a person alone in a room waiting for time to pass. i don't see the point in any of it. it just feels like a constant, draining weight that i can't shake off. i just want the weight to stop.",
